Info
====
This package contains a library for server side GUI construction which runs in a browser, using Javascript. It has been built by Bert Massop and Gerben van Veenendaal, see the original git repo from which this a fork intented to build correctly and run. For now, this repo just prevents bitrot of the original repo.

Installation and running
========================
For example:

> cabal-dev install
> dist/build/snapexample/snapexample

and open a browser on http://0.0.0.0:9000/

Status
======
[20130128] I got it to run on in Chrome and Firefox, not Safari. However, no windows/graphics were displayed, only text.
